ementor-element elementor-element-618490ff e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"618490ff\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4ced74 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f4ced74\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59b6c01e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"59b6c01e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15e1c6c about-us-text elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"15e1c6c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Join Level Up\u2019s free online bystander intervention training and learn how to safely interrupt harassment in public, at work, in your family or in your community.<\/p><p>We provide practical, feminist-led training sessions that equip you with the skills to intervene in cases of sexist, racist, LGBTQ+ or Islamophobic harassment and gender-based violence.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0479da3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0479da3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What the training is<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-161fd223 about-us-text elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"161fd223\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The fight for gender justice takes real action on a daily basis, but sometimes it\u2019s hard to know what that looks like.<\/p><p>That\u2019s why Level Up runs free online bystander intervention sessions \u2013 to give everyone the skills they need to intervene when they see harassment happening.<\/p><p>In the past year, we\u2019ve trained 413 people, and we\u2019re running more sessions in 2023!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-23e3a05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"23e3a05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why we run it<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d6ace6 about-us-text elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2d6ace6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Violence in our society \u2013 from sexist or racist harassment and domestic abuse to LGBTQ+ or Islamophobic hate crime \u2013 will not be prevented through more policing.\u00a0It will only be prevented if we all take action. We protect us, we keep each other safe.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b03348c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1b03348c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56fc447 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"56fc447\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div